      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI reported on three systematically refined meshes; GCI below 5 % on hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation performed; GCI on NIH is 8.3 % at the highest-shear operating point, exceeding the 5 % threshold. Achieved level 3 does not satisfy required level 4."
