    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lead-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile binding rules, the UnitOfAssurance is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier with the understanding that all 13 credibility factors have been evaluated and documented. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain as epistemic gaps flagged for resolution in a subsequent MRL-5 assessment cycle. The inline Requirement object (https://uofa.net/synth/req/mrl5-hemolysis-acceptance-threshold) is referenced within the validation results and captures the NIH ±15 % acceptance threshold. The assessment team acknowledges that achieved levels fall below required levels across all assessed factors and that additional V&V activities are mandated before regulatory acceptance of the hemolysis predictions for the Class III VAD indication.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
  },
